{"tid":1733755,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[悲報] 火鳳燎原慘遭3D動畫化","createTime":"2019-11-18T07:27:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T14:58:42.000Z","uid":49391,"like":3,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e9788daa99c3fa0ff25c992e332bf48fa8b24cc1","tid":1733755,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:27:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oON1543.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoON1543.jpg&h=d3f9b797&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港漫畫家陳某以三國時代為題材的漫畫作品《火鳳燎原》現正式宣布動畫化，首支3D風格的PV預告片也已公佈。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/bangumi/play/ep291879\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilibili.com%2Fbangumi%2Fplay%2Fep291879&d=uhXF1s3LJRzyxl6IDZpy2QZ9jGrNtOn8RK6k%2FrDhOJo%3D&h=00bbdf74\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bilibili.com/bangumi/play/ep291879</a><br />\n《火鳳燎原》有別於一般的三國漫畫，由於在人物和故事上描寫得極為細緻，因此其故事中的時間發展亦較為緩慢，作者陳某曾稱其作品完成日期可能長達十年。其畫風和分鏡方法均比較接近日本流行的作畫方式，相對上較為纖細。這種風格在充斥著武打漫畫的漫畫雜誌的香港不常見，這亦是陳某早年轉向台灣發展的原因之一。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0aTXEp5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0aTXEp5.jpg&h=9510fc8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y544jp6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY544jp6.jpg&h=3cede64a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NNYkCbT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNNYkCbT.jpg&h=9ca412ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nQFnQwT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnQFnQwT.jpg&h=086091fd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e274d676c2e5c8a9b717708f628798c503a4724a","tid":1733755,"uid":261132,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:28:56.000Z","msg":"成個屎艷文布袋戲咁,你睇埋我果份"},{"pid":"76df3e15addbd035c9415a523c29168e439d9c88","tid":1733755,"uid":29080,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"repl